<sect1>Compilation and installation
<p>

In order to compile and install Term on your system, type the following in
the base directory of the Term distribution:

<tscreen><verb>
% ./configure
% make
% make install
</verb></tscreen>

<p>
Since Term uses <verb>autoconf</verb> you should have not trouble
compiling it.
Should you run into problems please report them to the the author at 
<htmlurl url="mailto:lms@mpn.nu" name = "Lars M Sandig">


